item.description: Computer vision at Zyl Zyl is an app aiming at finding the best pictures lost in the limbo of your phone. This post explains why we are introducing computer vision algorithms in the app. A picture is worth a thousand words Ever wanted to remember forever the crazy atmosphere of Saturday’s party with your friends? The liberating moment when you graduate? The cuteness of your cat chasing a laser beam?
